## 2026-03-28 - styleSync.ts re-fetches ALL Figma styles from scratch for every single token
- Cached style lists upfront: `applyStyles` now fetches paint/text/effect styles once via `figma.getLocalPaintStylesAsync()` etc., stores them in a `StyleCache` object, and passes the cache to each per-type applicator. Newly created styles are pushed into the cache arrays so subsequent tokens can find them without re-fetching.
- Replaced all 6 `any` type annotations with proper discriminated union types (`StyleToken = ColorStyleToken | GradientStyleToken | TypographyStyleToken | ShadowStyleToken`) using core DTCG types from `@tokenmanager/core`.
- Typed the `readFigmaStyles` output tokens with `ReadStyleToken` union (`ReadColorToken | ReadTypographyToken | ReadShadowToken`).

